Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:57.15,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}為了故作平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:02.91,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\an2\pos(960,1065)}行為舉止的算式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:06.33,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\an2\pos(960,1065)}解個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:12.53,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如果這就是戀愛
